resources.string: "MusicMojo is a rock band with a soundscape built upon elements of folk and classic sounds widespread, at times, with layers of progressive, pop, ambient and electronic textures creating a unique music experience that is truly global in nature but local in idea."

Thomas William-Violistt 
 Jacob Liam - lead Guitar 
 Samuel Logan - Singer 
 Raphel Gabriel - Keyboard 
 Zack Mathis - Drums 
 Lucas Justin - Singer
MusicMojo was a 15 member ensemble cast the bands strength lies in its versatality and predictability. Thanks to 7 vocalists and 6 instrumentalist from the length the breadth of the world.
